title: Graph Theory has many applications.One of the most common application is to find the shortest distance between one city to another. We all know that to reach your PC, this web-page had to travel many routers from the server. Graph Theory helps it to find out the routers that needed to be crossed. During war, which street needs to be bombarded to disconnect the capital city from others, that too can be found out using Graph Theory.
